title: RHONJ: Nashville Hot Stricken
description:
The Real Housewives of New Jersey head to Nashville, and it goes about as well as you'd expect, which is to say not very well at all. Watch out for flying Palomas!!

Check out this recap with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/65106644

Get tix to our live shows: https://www.watchwhatcrappens.com/10th-anniversary-hunky-dory-tour/
